phrases: Oh man, what have I done?
Who knows how much this IV drip will cost?
Who cares if I recover thanks to this?
Um, I would just like to confirm this one more time.
National Health Insurance will cover this, right?
Well then, let us hook you up to another bag.
This is why I told you to stay in bed!
You are getting two more now!
You are the absurd one here!
It all starts right here, right now
Let us picture what we can do
Let us picture what we can do
Let us picture what we can do
But we can overcome them all
But we can overcome them all
But we can overcome them all
Our dreams are born from nothing
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
I want to spread my wings
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
We will be the ones to choose and decide the future
Let us chase after our dreams
There will be times when we cry
I have a really important wish
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
Surrender the sacred sword, Better Half.
What do you expect me to do?
I am sure it is the sword itself that is rejecting you here.
Humans are not meant to possess the sacred sword.
It must be returned to us.
More importantly, Chiho does not have anything to do with this, does she?
as a human from another world who knows who the Overlord really is
yet still has feelings for him.
We can use her as a research subject for how the Overlord's power affects human bodies.
How dare you speak to me, Archangel Sariel, in that manner?!
Can your body hold out any longer?
I consider myself chivalrous, you know?
Do not force me to do any more.
A lady should not scream like that.
Oh, looks like an insect has crawled its way over.
As he is now, even you can beat him by yourself.
The Overlord and I will perish in another world,
and Ente Isla will not change a bit from before you came here.
Are you really okay with that?
I am the symbolic angel of the Investigation Commission,
and I guarantee the legitimacy of your actions.
I do not wish to sacrifice anyone anymore!
What the hell do you have against Dullahan?!
Do you have any idea how much getting a new bike is going to cost me?!
What do you think you are doing?
You probably do not get it, since you do not work.
MgRonald's uniforms are lent to their employees.
If you damage them for reasons unrelated to work,
you will have to pay for them.
Castle Overlord's treasury cannot afford it!
What are you doing in public, you deviant?!
You are the one who did this!
You bravely came all the way to Japan,
boldly stayed next door, and treated us to good food,
so I figured I would overlook most things.
However, you are now getting in my way and hurting one of my staff!
As the assistant manager, I cannot let you get away with this!
You would realized who I was?
In what universe would a lovely lady suddenly move in next door to a bunch of guys and take care of them?
There are still some leftovers from what Suzuno cooked.
It stinks of sacred powers, but food is food.
Looks like it affected Ashiya quite a bit, though.
I thought you could get along with Emi, and I had high hopes for you,
but in the end, you are no different from Olba, huh?
You may dress it up in pretty words,
but you do not care what you have to destroy for power, do you?
If the end justifies any means,
then how exactly are you lot any different from us demons?
You went to Fushima Park with them.
You helped with the flea market.
You would finally gotten closer to Emi and Chiho, but you got them mixed up in this mess.
Are you not ashamed of yourself?
I used up most of my powers to break through that barrier.
I will be on my way, then.
He is not someone you can beat as you are now.
What, you in cahoots with someone else?
No wonder Emi could not beat him.
He gets stronger the closer he is to the moon.
You do not stand a one-in-a-million chance of beating him without your powers.
Why would you go that far?
Chiho's a colleague I should protect
I am not shameless enough to abandon my employees and run away.
Besides, you are hoping for it too, are not you?
That is why you did not stop Chiho from calling me, right?
Well, I do not really care either way.
Why do you say such things?
If the Overlord speaks to me that way...
I will not be able to stay shameless now, will I?
He is definitely gotten mixed up in some trouble.
What is he even doing at the Tokyo Government Office?
Did he abandon Emilia and come back home?
Nice life you are leading there.
Do you wish to return to the heavens?
I will grant that wish of yours.
If I cannot retrieve the sacred sword even after doing all this,
I guess I have no choice but to extract it directly from inside you.
What are you going to do?!
I will take it directly from your body.
I am going to collect the heavenly silver that the sacred sword, Better Half, is made of.
What do you think you are doing to Yusa?!
In the first place, I am not interested in modest women like her.
One could say you are more my type, actually.
I will examine your entire body later, too.
Every nook and cranny of it.
You are a fucking hopeless sleazebag!
Just you try laying a finger on Chiho.
I appreciate that you are spirited,
but what can you do to stop me?
I am not talking about myself.
Maou will not let you get away if you did anything to her.
Hero Emilia's going to rely on the Overlord to save her?
You set up shop opposite MgRonald's.
It is a boss's job to protect his employees from danger.
Have you lost your mind, Emilia?
Do you seriously think the Overlord's bound to how this world works?
He is not bound to it.
He is going along with it out of his own free will.
That is the kind of man A-ranked employee of MgRonald's Hatagaya Station branch,
and shift supervisor Maou Sadao is!
An Overlord who has the trust of the Hero?
Sorry I kept you waiting, Chiho.
Looks like Emi's in one piece, too.
Who would have thought you would really come to save them?
I did not expect the perfume-wearing midget manager to have the Radiance of the Fallen's Heinous Eyes, either.
I need to retrieve the sacred sword, you see.
Better Half is made out of the Heavenly Silver of Progress, which is Heaven's most prized asset.
We cannot let the Hero hold on to it forever.
What I find unforgivable is that you hurt one of my colleagues.
How dare you put Chiho through a harrowing experience!
Chiho's a precious employee of mine.
As the Overlord, and the shift supervisor,
What can you do with that frail body of yours?
How much can you take with what little magic you have left?
I wonder how long you can keep that up!
Dammit, I cannot do shit without my powers.
I get stronger the closer I am to the moon.
You are in big trouble, Overlord.
O holy spirits that bind life and time.
May this world find itself beyond the stars.
You thought he might be able to gather magic from people's fear and anger?
It is too late for that.
I can almost touch the moon!
No one can beat me now that I have gained this much power.
Does not that mean things have gotten crazy down there?
I managed to replenish my powers thanks to that, too.
Control those absurd powers of yours a little, will you?!
Do you want to kill Chiho?!
Are you seriously going to fight like that?!
This underwear's made with cutting-edge material that can handle anything!
Just how much do you trust your damn underwear?!
Take care of them for me.
Are you out of your mind, Bell?!
You are siding with the Overlord?!
Is burdening the populace with a false peace,
causing mayhem in a different world,
and betraying those that follow your faith
truly the justice that God exemplifies?!
As the chief investigator of the Commission,
I cannot turn a blind eye to that false brand of justice!
You are just the Inquisition's bloodthirsty reaper!
How dare you speak of justice?!
At the very least, the life the Overlord's
No, the life Maou Sadao's leading here in Japan
does not oppose the concept of justice!
There is still nobody out there who can beat me now that I have gained the power of this massive moon!
I would not be so sure.
Now Lord Sariel will finish the Overlord off.
can you give me Emilia's bag?
What are you going to do with it?
I will give it back to Emilia, obviously.
She will kill me if I do not.
Heaven is a place on Earth.
It exists in a certain six tatami mat, second floor apartment.
Being a bum is the best.
It is all up to you now, Maou.
As a benevolent Overlord, I will let you choose.
Will you run away with your tail between your legs?
Or will you pay for this by becoming my punching bag?
I will kill you and accomplish what I came here to do!
An Overlord who can only gain magic by doping on people's negative emotions is no Overlord at all!
I do not have the energy for this today, thanks to that pervert tormenting me.
Once I get the sacred sword back, I will have his head!
You may be invincible against those who use sacred powers,
You may be invincible against those who use sacred powers,
but you should have picked who to fight more wisely.
You can have my unholy sword.
Aww man, he went and destroyed a bunch of places.
I finally got my powers back, yet I will have to burn it all to fix this shit again?!
It is your fault for taking your sweet time.
You do not sound very grateful after I went out of my way to save you.
What do you mean, more importantly?!
This is a matter of life and death!
I returned to base to don my mantle.
What the hell are you even here for?!
Just put on some clothes already!
You cannot go back like that, Maou!
I want to eat some chicken.
Where in this silent sky does the sun rise?
A promise I made while pretending to not see it
Being a liar and a coward
If I was at fault for everything
Then our promise might only have been a fleeting dream
I managed to hide it in the shadow of the moonlight
My tears will not flow anymore
If I was able to let everything go
I might be able to cry again
But this world is full of things I want to protect
